name: Varför gömmer du dig i häcken?
original_name: Varför gömmer du dig i häcken?
overview: "Why are you hiding in the hedge?" - a Swedish version of the satirist Lenny Bruce's exuberant humor, obscenities and social criticism, embodied by actor Jarl Kulle.
